</div>";s:14:"date_timestamp";i:1349948731;}i:13;a:10:{s:5:"title";s:40:"Views' Javascript is not keyboard-usable";s:4:"link";s:30:"http://drupal.org/node/1806308";s:11:"description";s:1207:"<p>Part of meta issues <span class="project-issue-status-1 project-issue-status-info"><a href="/node/1805996" title="Status: active">#1805996: [META] Views in Drupal Core</a></span> and <span class="project-issue-status-1 project-issue-status-info"><a href="/node/1802678" title="Status: active">#1802678: [META] Views: accessibility review</a></span>.</p>
<p>Test whether Views' Javascript is keyboard-usable.</p>
<h4>Steps</h4>
<ol><li>Test this issue using 8.x HEAD:<br /><div class="codeblock"><code>git clone --recursive --branch 8.x http://git.drupal.org/project/drupal.git</code></div></li>
<li>Enable Views and Views UI.</li>
<li>Test each screen of the Views UI, including: the administrative view listing, the view creation wizard, the advanced administrative interface, and modal dialogs.</li>
<li>Test using only your keyboard (unplug your mouse). Verify that the UI can be fully operated using only a keyboard. (<a href="http://drupal.org/core-gates#gatev3-javascript" rel="nofollow">More about JavaScript accessibility</a>)</li>
<li>Report any problems in this issue.</li>
</ol><p>Reference: <a href="http://drupal.org/core-gates#accessibility" rel="nofollow">core accessibility gate</a>.</p>
";s:8:"comments";s:39:"http://drupal.org/node/1806308#comments";s:8:"category";s:52:"accessibilityJavaScriptNeeds manual testingNoviceVDC";s:7:"pubdate";s:31:"Mon, 08 Oct 2012 12:03:11 +0000";s:2:"dc";a:1:{s:7:"creator";s:3:"xjm";}s:4:"guid";s:28:"1806308 at http://drupal.org";s:7:"summary";s:1207:"<p>Part of meta issues <span class="project-issue-status-1 project-issue-status-info"><a href="/node/1805996" title="Status: active">#1805996: [META] Views in Drupal Core</a></span> and <span class="project-issue-status-1 project-issue-status-info"><a href="/node/1802678" title="Status: active">#1802678: [META] Views: accessibility review</a></span>.</p>
<p>Test whether Views' Javascript is keyboard-usable.</p>
<h4>Steps</h4>
<ol><li>Test this issue using 8.x HEAD:<br /><div class="codeblock"><code>git clone --recursive --branch 8.x http://git.drupal.org/project/drupal.git</code></div></li>
<li>Enable Views and Views UI.</li>
<li>Test each screen of the Views UI, including: the administrative view listing, the view creation wizard, the advanced administrative interface, and modal dialogs.</li>
