";s:14:"date_timestamp";i:1319487600;}i:43;a:10:{s:5:"title";s:94:"Make tabledrag warning message show when row weights are enabled, and add WAI-ARIA live region";s:4:"link";s:30:"http://drupal.org/node/1272990";s:11:"description";s:1123:"<p>In <span class="project-issue-status-5 project-issue-status-info"><a href="/node/504378" title="Status: closed (won't fix)">#504378: Auto-save draggable forms</a></span> I found out that:</p>
<blockquote><p>
